                  <a href="https://github.com/LukePepin" style="color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:underline;">[ GitHub Profile ]</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="profile-card">
            <div class="avatar"><img src="/assets/photos/andrew-muszynski.webp" alt="Andrew Muszynski" /></div>
            <div class="profile-meta">
              <strong>Andrew Muszynski</strong>
              <a href="mailto:muszynskiandrew@uri.edu">muszynskiandrew@uri.edu</a>
              <p>Optimizes multi-agent coordination in smart factory layouts.</p>
              <div style="margin-top:0.5rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap; font-size:0.85rem;">
                  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrew-muszynski-2b3217223/" style="color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:underline;">[ LinkedIn ]</a>
