            <div class="profile-meta">
              <strong>Harishjitu Saseendran</strong>
              <a href="mailto:hsaseendran@uri.edu">hsaseendran@uri.edu</a>
              <p>Studies genetic machine learning algorithms for manufacturing process optimization.</p>
              <div style="margin-top:0.5rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap; font-size:0.85rem;">
                  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/harishjitu/" style="color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:underline;">[ LinkedIn ]</a>
                  <a href="https://github.com/hsaseendran" style="color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:underline;">[ GitHub Profile ]</a>
