            <div class="profile-meta">
              <strong>Jay-Sun Rutledge</strong>
              <a href="mailto:jaysun_rutledge@uri.edu">jaysun_rutledge@uri.edu</a>
              <p>Builds computer vision systems for manufacturing quality control.</p>
