          <article class="profile-card">
            <div class="avatar"><img src="/assets/photos/josh-fishbein.webp" alt="Josh Fishbein" /></div>
            <div class="profile-meta">
              <strong>Josh Fishbein</strong>
              <a href="mailto:joshfish9182@uri.edu">joshfish9182@uri.edu</a>
              <p>Researching discriminate laser polishing methods.</p>
              <div style="margin-top:0.5rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap; font-size:0.85rem;">
