                  <a href="https://github.com/joshfish9182" style="color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:underline;">[ GitHub Profile ]</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="profile-card">
            <div class="avatar"><img src="/assets/photos/seamus-okeefe.JPG" alt="Seamus O'Keefe" /></div>
            <div class="profile-meta">
              <strong>Seamus O'Keefe</strong>
              <a href="mailto:seamus.okeefe@uri.edu">seamus.okeefe@uri.edu</a>
              <p>Developing cost optimazation strategy through simulation.</p>
              <div style="margin-top:0.5rem; display:flex; gap:0.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap; font-size:0.85rem;">
                  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/seamus-o-keefe/" style="color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:underline;">[ LinkedIn ]</a>
                  <a href="https://github.com/okeefeseamus-stack" style="color:var(--text-muted); text-decoration:underline;">[ GitHub Profile ]</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="profile-section">
        <h2>Undergraduate Researchers</h2>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <article class="profile-card">
            <div class="avatar"><img src="/assets/photos/andrew-oxley.webp" alt="Andrew Oxley" /></div>
            <div class="profile-meta">
